  "title": "Health Attendant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Highlights:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Location: </strong>Novena</li><li><strong>Working Days & Hours</strong>: 12 Hours Shift / 4 days work 2 days off</li><li><strong>Commitment Period</strong>: up to 30 Jun 2026</li></ul><p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Discharge Cleaning</strong>: Perform bed discharge cleaning after patient discharge or transfers, including at night.</li><li><strong>General Cleaning</strong>: Clear rubbish, clean various areas including the ward, lift lobby, toilets, wheelchairs, trolleys, and more.</li><li><strong>Ward Maintenance</strong>: Keep the ward pantry and fridge clean and tidy.</li><li><strong>Meal Assistance</strong>: Help prepare and serve meals and beverages to patients.</li><li><strong>Supply Management</strong>: Store linen and other supplies properly, reporting shortages as needed.</li><li><strong>PPE Management</strong>: Ensure PPE supplies and patient pyjamas are topped up and distributed.</li><li><strong>Patient Care</strong>: Assist nursing staff in looking after fall-risk patients and aid in patient transfers.</li><li><strong>Replenishment Tasks</strong>: Refill PPE, hand rub, and Critical Care Carts.</li><li><strong>Support Duties</strong>: Undertake any other support duties required by the department.</li></ul><p><strong>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. Thank you.</strong></p><p><em>By submitting your resume, you consent to the handling of your personal data in accordance with Certis Group Privacy Policy (www.certisgroup.com/privacy-policy).</em></p>",
